27:49.585 --> 27:51.553
and I'm thinking, "How?

27:51.670 --> 27:55.095
How could I allow someone
to cut into my eye with a knife?

27:55.215 --> 27:57.559
Cut into the window to my soul?"

27:57.676 --> 27:59.553
