don't you think I'd rather sit at home...

28:10.898 --> 28:12.775
<i>and be able to make things up?</i>

28:12.900 --> 28:14.902
<i>It'd be so much less
wear and tear on my body.</i>

28:15.068 --> 28:16.945
<i>But I'm thinking,
"I need my right eye."</i>

28:17.070 --> 28:19.414
What would happen
if I went blind in my right eye?

28:19.531 --> 28:22.751
