29:07.454 --> 29:10.503
And I walk over,
and the prostitutes part like the Red Sea...

29:10.624 --> 29:12.752
and I walk up
to this old black Pontiac...

29:12.876 --> 29:14.878
and it's got three Hasidic Jews in it -

29:15.003 --> 29:16.880
two in the front, one in the back.

29:17.005 --> 29:19.224
And they say, "Get in."

29:20.842 --> 29:22.344
And I do...

29:22.469 --> 29:24.471
because I'm curious...

29:24.638 --> 29:26.982
and I love to be wanted.

29:27.140 --> 29:31.190
So I get in the back with the youngest,
and they drive off down the Bowery.

29:31.311 --> 29:35.361
The prostitutes are yelling,
"Bye! Have a good trick!"

29:35.482 --> 29:37.701
So I don't know -
