34:10.422 --> 34:12.641
So I say, "Azaria...

34:12.759 --> 34:15.478
you mean to say
you have two bodies -

34:15.594 --> 34:17.554
one that can stand up
and look back at the other -

34:17.639 --> 34:19.607
and you've never tried
to make love to yourself?"

34:19.766 --> 34:21.438
I mean, that's the first thing
