35:02.934 --> 35:04.974
If I could come like that
without touching myself...

35:04.978 --> 35:08.482
I'd be a happy man -
or at least content."

35:08.648 --> 35:11.322
So she tells me
I have to lie on the floor, right?

35:11.484 --> 35:13.737
And I have to suck
the energy in the room -

35:13.862 --> 35:17.412
