35:59.074 --> 36:00.872
Listen to me.
Come out to Minneapolis...

36:01.034 --> 36:03.114
and we'll have
a Native American sweat lodge for you.

36:03.203 --> 36:05.501
And the power of our prayer -
it's larger than one-on-one.

36:05.622 --> 36:08.501
It's a group. You must come."
