36:08.625 --> 36:10.593
"No. Look me in the face
and tell me you'll come."

36:10.710 --> 36:13.384
"Well, I'll give it a try."
"No. Look me in the eyes now."

36:13.505 --> 36:15.473
I look her in the face,
and her entire face...

36:15.590 --> 36:18.059
