36:24.724 --> 36:26.601
I will come out to Minneapolis.

36:26.726 --> 36:28.694
I'll do it. I'll come."

36:28.812 --> 36:32.316
I think I would try
an Indian sweat ceremony.

36:32.440 --> 36:35.990
I don't think it could be much stranger
than my trip to the hypnotherapist.

36:36.111 --> 36:40.332
And maybe it'd be more successful.
Who knows?

36:40.448 --> 36:42.325
I don't think so.

36:42.450 --> 36:45.374
An Indian sweat ceremony?
Never heard of it.

36:45.495 --> 36:47.463
That's a pretty mystic idea.

36:47.580 --> 36:50.834
An Indian sweat ceremony?

36:50.959 --> 36:53.007
It sounds interesting,
but I don't think so.

36:53.128 --> 36:55.631
